  "description_snippet": "**VULNERABILITY DETAILS**   \n  \nAn extension with the <all_urls> permission can read any file on the file system and send it's content to a remote host, using chrome.tabs.captureVisibleTab although extension (Allow access to file URLs) is disabled.  \n  \nthis bug is a fork of https://bugs.chromium.or"
